title: Active Knee Extension
description: Knee extension strengthens muscles in front of thigh and shin. Lie supine on mat and bend knee at right angle.

title: Heel Slides
description: The heel slide is a mobility exercise to increase the range of knee flexion at the joint.

title: Active Hamstrings
description: Hamstring curls strengthen the muscles in the back of the thigh.

title: Sitting Knee Flexion
description: Knee flexion help increase the range of motion available at the joint.

title: Inner-Range Quad Sitting
description: Inner Range Quadriceps exercise helps strengthen the muscles around the knee.

title: Quadriceps Stretch
description: The quadriceps exercise will help strengthen the quadriceps muscles resulting in increased flexibility, improved circulation, and reduced stress.

title: Calf Raise Step Up
description: This exercise helps strengthen the cold muscles and lower leg.

title: Passive Knee Bend
description: This exercise helps improve mobility in a stiff knee joint.

title: Football Kick for Knee
description: This exercise helps strengthen the cold muscles and lower leg.

title: Hamstring Curl (band)
description: This exercise helps strengthen hamstring muscle group.

title: VMO Split Squat
description: This exercise helps strengthen the lower body and improve knee stability.

title: VMO Adductor Strengthening
description: This exercise helps strengthen the muscle surrounding the kneecap and stabilize the patella.

title: Hip Flexion Lying
description: This exercise helps mobilize the hip joint and strengthen the hip flexor muscles.

title: Leg Lift Glute Strengthen
description: This exercise predominantly strengthens the gluteal (buttock) muscles the and lower back muscles on the side you are lifting

title: Flexion Arm Lift
description: This exercise will help mobilize elbow joint.

title: Elbow Flexion Standing
description: This exercise will help mobilize elbow joint.

title: Full Flexion Sit Up
description: This exercise will help strengthen the abdominal muscles.
